name: Slate
text:
Do Kristy, Mary Anne, Claudia, and Stacy mean anything to you?

If they do, join us tomorrow for our Babysitter's Club special with @Netflix showrunner @RachelShukert & @HeatherTwit. Don't be late—unless you want to get on Kristy's bad side.
